OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772806275
OL,3,CMonkey found in car during prison
OL,4,Cdrugs crackdown
OL,6,FPolice found a monkey in a car during
OL,7,Fan operation to stop drugs getting
OL,8,Finto prison.
OL,10,FThe year-old marmoset, believed to be
OL,11,Fa domestic pet, was discovered when
OL,12,Fofficers stopped the vehicle outside
OL,13,FHMP Moorlands in Doncaster.
OL,15,FA South Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,16,Fsaid: "The monkey was safely removed
OL,17,Ffrom the vehicle and transported to an
OL,18,Fanimal sanctuary, with the RSPCA now
OL,19,Fcarrying out further enquiries."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
