OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1772806275
OL,3,CMonkey found in car during prison
OL,4,Cdrugs crackdown
OL,6,FPolice were carrying out checks as
OL,7,Fpart of Operation Gartley, where
OL,8,Fvisitors to Doncaster prisons are
OL,9,Fsearched before entering.
OL,11,FOfficers also found a quantity of
OL,12,Fcrack cocaine.
OL,14,FTwo women in their 20s were arrested
OL,15,Fon suspicion of possession with intent
OL,16,Fto supply drugs.
OL,18,FAbout 5,000 primates are kept as pets
OL,19,Fin the UK, but from April keepers new
OL,20,Flegislation will need to obtain a
OL,21,Flicence from their local authority.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
